riodPair.summable_weierstrassPExceptSummand\"><span class=\"name\">PeriodPair</span>.<span class=\"name\">summable_weierstrassPExceptSummand</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">L</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair\">PeriodPair</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l₀ </span><span class=\"fn\">z </span><span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hx</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <span class=\"fn\">↥<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">L</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair.lattice\">lattice</a></span></span>), <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">l</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Ne\">≠</a> <span class=\"fn\">l₀</span> → <a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#Norm.norm\">‖</a><span class=\"fn\">z</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSub.hSub\">-</a> <span class=\"fn\">x</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#Norm.norm\">‖</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LT.lt\">&lt;</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#Norm.norm\">‖</a><span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">l</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSub.hSub\">-</a> <span class=\"fn\">x</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#Norm.norm\">‖</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/InfiniteSum/Defs.html#Summable\">Summable</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Data/Function.html#Function.uncurry\">Function.uncurry</a> <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>) (<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\">↥<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">L</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair.lattice\">lattice</a></span></span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">L</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair.weierstrassPExceptSummand\">weierstrassPExceptSummand</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">l₀</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span> <span class=\"fn\">b</span> <span class=\"fn\">c</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> (<span class=\"fn\">z</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSub.hSub\">-</a> <span class=\"fn\">x</span>) <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HPow.hPow\">^</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span></span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"In the power series expansion of `℘(z) = ∑ᵢ aᵢ (z - x)ⁱ` at some `x ∉ L`,\neach `aᵢ` can be writen as a sum over `l ∈ L`, i.e.\n`aᵢ = ∑ₗ, (i + 1) * (l - x)⁻ⁱ⁻²` for `i ≠ 0` and `a₀ = ∑ₗ, (l - x)⁻² - l⁻²`.\n\nWe show that the double sum converges if `z` falls in a ball centered at `x` that doesn't touch `L`.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair.summable_weierstrassPExceptSummand","kind":"theorem","line":666,"name":"PeriodPair.summable_weierstrassPExceptSummand","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.lean#L666-L724"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair.coeff_weierstrassPExceptSeries\"><span class=\"name\">PeriodPair</span>.<span class=\"name\">coeff_weierstrassPExceptSeries</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">L</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair\">PeriodPair</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l₀ </span><span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">L</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair.weierstrassPExceptSeries\">weierstrassPExceptSeries</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">l₀</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span>)</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/FormalMultilinearSeries.html#FormalMultilinearSeries.coeff\">coeff</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/InfiniteSum/Defs.html#tsum\">∑'</a> (<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <span class=\"fn\">↥<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">L</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair.lattice\">lattice</a></span></span>)<a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/InfiniteSum/Defs.html#tsum\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">L</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair.weierstrassPExceptSummand\">weierstrassPExceptSummand</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">l₀</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span> <span class=\"fn\">l</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair.coeff_weierstrassPExceptSeries","kind":"theorem","line":642,"name":"PeriodPair.coeff_weierstrassPExceptSeries","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.lean#L642-L663"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair.weierstrassPExceptSeries\"><span class=\"name\">PeriodPair</span>.<span class=\"name\">weierstrassPExceptSeries</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">L</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair\">PeriodPair</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l₀ </span><span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Calculus/FormalMultilinearSeries.html#FormalMultilinearSeries\">FormalMultilinearSeries</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The power series expansion of `℘[L - l₀]` at `x`.\nSee `PeriodPair.hasFPowerSeriesOnBall_weierstrassPExcept`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair.weierstrassPExceptSeries","kind":"def","line":634,"name":"PeriodPair.weierstrassPExceptSeries","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.lean#L634-L639"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Elliptic/Weierstrass.html#PeriodPair.weierstrassPExceptSummand\"><span class=\"name\">PeriodPair</span>.<span class=\"name\">weierstrassPExceptSummand</span></a>